  <Docs>
    <summary>Supports mappings between .NET types and XML Schema data types.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 `XmlMapping` is the base class for the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlTypeMapping> and <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMembersMapping> classes. It supports built-in and custom XML schema data types, plus SOAP encoding (Section 5 of the SOAP 1.1 specification). Use the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlTypeMapping> or <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMemberMapping> class instead of deriving a class directly from `XmlMapping`.
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
